descript.abstract: This polygon data layer represents municipalities for Trempealeau County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Trempealeau_Municipalities_2014.gdb. [Polygon coverage of political boundaries]
descript.purpose: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [For use in an Enhanced 9-1-1 system.]
descript.supplinf: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For current dataset download, please visit http://www.tremplocounty.com/tchome/landrecords/data.aspx [Used as reference for determining if a location is in the county or city.]
